parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected failure of the windshield can cause a loss of visibility, distraction, and potentially lead to accidents, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The windshield cracks or shatters without apparent reason
cracks appear suddenly
cracks grow over time
small pebbles or stones cause significant damage to the windshield
windshields are prone to chipping or cracking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The frequent occurrence of windshield chips and cracks can compromise the structural integrity of the windshield, posing a safety risk to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: Windshield develops chips or cracks
even with minor impacts
such as small stones or pebbles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Android Auto navigation system can cause a security and safety hazard, especially at night, as it can lead to disorientation and confusion while driving.
symptoms: The navigation system freezes
points in the wrong direction
lags behind the actual position
or shows a lost GPS signal; frequent disconnections and reconnections of the USB cable are required to resolve the issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle catching fire after a collision, such as hitting a deer, can result in a total loss of the vehicle and pose a significant risk to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The vehicle catches fire immediately after a collision
resulting in a total loss of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, especially when the vehicle is in a parking lot or in close proximity to obstacles.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates unexpectedly while the brake pedal is depressed
the vehicle jumps a curb
the vehicle crashes into an object
the vehicle accelerates backward independently while the brake pedal is depressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can cause the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly, leading to loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal is depressed
but the vehicle accelerates instead of slowing down
the vehicle accelerates backward independently while the brake pedal is depressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the vehicle control system can cause the vehicle to accelerate unexpectedly, leading to loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates unexpectedly while the brake pedal is depressed
the vehicle jumps a curb
the vehicle crashes into an object
the vehicle accelerates backward independently while the brake pedal is depressed.
